<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1030482-why-does-don-jaime-trust-carceles-with-the">Why does Don Jaime trust Carceles with the secret papers?

We&#39;re talking about a loudmouth radical or loose cannon who talks about guillotining the establishment.

Don Jaime was a traditionalist so wouldn&#39;t it make more sense for him to put his trust in Don Lucas?</a>
</div>
