<span id="freeTextContainer12629731493350400526">This was mediocre, at best. Very nice use of language but the plot was horribly dull with a disappointing outcome. If this was supposed to have the added benefit of convincing people that good things come out of European literature, it was a failure. Better that they stick to Simenon for short thrillers or detective stories and leave this sort of stuff on the shelf.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


