<li class='cover' id='bookCover_13641537'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/13641537-the-high-blue-arena"><img alt="The High Blue Arena" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/book/111x148-bcc042a9c91a29c1d680899eff700a03.png" />
